@host = http://localhost:5099

### Libros — listado
GET {{host}}/api/Books
Accept: application/json

### Libros — obtener por id
GET {{host}}/api/Books/1
Accept: application/json

### Libros — crear
POST {{host}}/api/Books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Libro de ejemplo",
  "description": "Un libro de ejemplo creado desde el archivo .http.",
  "pageCount": 250,
  "excerpt": "Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet.",
  "publishDate": "2026-01-15T00:00:00Z"
}

### Libros — actualizar
PUT {{host}}/api/Books/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "title": "Libro actualizado",
  "description": "Descripción actualizada.",
  "pageCount": 300,
  "excerpt": "Extracto actualizado.",
  "publishDate": "2026-02-01T00:00:00Z"
}

### Libros — eliminar
DELETE {{host}}/api/Books/1

### Autores — listado (con bookCount agregado)
GET {{host}}/api/Authors
Accept: application/json

### Autores — obtener por id
GET {{host}}/api/Authors/1
Accept: application/json

### Autores — por libro
GET {{host}}/api/Authors/by-book/1
Accept: application/json

### Autores — crear
POST {{host}}/api/Authors
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idBook": 1,
  "firstName": "Ada",
  "lastName": "Lovelace"
}

### Autores — actualizar
PUT {{host}}/api/Authors/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "idBook": 1,
  "firstName": "Ada",
  "lastName": "Lovelace"
}

### Autores — eliminar
DELETE {{host}}/api/Authors/1
